OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening, with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, prolonged at times and
OL,8,Faccompanied by hill fog across western
OL,9,Fareas. Rain will become more
OL,10,Fintermittent later in the night,
OL,11,Fespecially in the east, some places
OL,12,Fbecoming dry by dawn. Breezy
OL,13,Fthroughout.
OL,14,
OL,15,CMonday:FRather cloudy initially but
OL,16,Fbecoming drier and brighter. The odd
OL,17,Fspot of rain cannot be ruled out,
OL,18,Fparticularly in the north. Feeling
OL,19,Fpleasantly warm in a light breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
