OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday, cloudy with spells of rain at
OL,7,Ftimes, mostly affecting western hills
OL,8,Fwith drier conditions further east.
OL,9,FWednesday and Thursday becoming drier
OL,10,Fand sunnier. Temperatures becoming
OL,11,Frather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
